{"tid":2060662,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得 不浪漫罪名 係抗爭歌黎","createTime":"2020-06-11T23:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T11:12:48.000Z","uid":82889,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb9ea053cbe043fc480ccb19557efd4e9dea38aa","tid":2060662,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:05:03.000Z","msg":"為何不浪漫亦是罪名 <span style=\"color: red;\">香港人點解一定要浪漫抗爭？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為何不轟烈是極壞事情 <span style=\"color: red;\">點解一定要有靚畫面？要人犧牲？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來未察覺我每個動作 <span style=\"color: red;\">手足食次m記就比人否定哂付出</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有聲都有愛你的摯證 <span style=\"color: red;\">手足所有日子都記得但唔係日日開口提</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來未察覺我語氣動聽 <span style=\"color: red;\">口中好多反諷表達無力感</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在我呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n甚麼都會用一生保證 <span style=\"color: red;\">其實手足就算食乜都好 都會記住左所有野 會用一生去抗爭</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f0f9dce94fb2f66f974bbc8e69e5c2af18f768","tid":2060662,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"估下王傑黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a551af04596f99517bb9baa9d3a3c0e84ab65c","tid":2060662,"uid":161498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2f0f9dce94fb2f66f974bbc8e69e5c2af18f768","tid":2060662,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"估下王傑黃定藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T23:31:52.000Z","msg":"改叫黃傑?"},{"pid":"61b6667717b848ef7771e82320c23a789a6c071f","tid":2060662,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a551af04596f99517bb9baa9d3